  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1848860/extras/c1982e3231648e1ea9296df202062068.avif?t=1660924251\" width=600 height=200 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1848860/extras/2985cba69493613028c6001621e484fe.poster.avif?t=1660924251\" width=600 height=368 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1848860/extras/2985cba69493613028c6001621e484fe.webm?t=1660924251\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1848860/extras/2985cba69493613028c6001621e484fe.mp4?t=1660924251\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong><i>NOTICE: Save data from the Ember Crusade IV Demo will carry over to the full game.</i></strong><br><br>Ember Crusade IV is a twin stick looter shooter roguelike where you embark on a blazing crusade to save the solar system from a demonic invasion.<br><br>Collect<strong> hundreds of guns, armor and materials</strong> to create the ultimate crusader. Take to the randomly generated battlefield, dodge rolling, shooting, reloading and pulverizing your enemies into a<i> very fine bloody pâté</i>. Ember Crusade IV features:<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong> Visceral combat</strong><br></li><li><strong> 7 Planets</strong><br></li><li> <strong>Hundreds of guns</strong><br></li><li> <strong>3 Powerful crusaders</strong></li></ul><br>Fight through seven distinct planets as one of three powerful crusaders: The <strong>Justicar</strong>, <strong>Marauder </strong>and <strong>Gunmancer</strong>. Each crusader brings a unique ability to the battlefield, like throwing holy hammers at enemies, or summoning guns made out of bone to fight alongside you.",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1848860/extras/c1982e3231648e1ea9296df202062068.avif?t=1660924251\" width=600 height=200 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1848860/extras/2985cba69493613028c6001621e484fe.poster.avif?t=1660924251\" width=600 height=368 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1848860/extras/2985cba69493613028c6001621e484fe.webm?t=1660924251\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1848860/extras/2985cba69493613028c6001621e484fe.mp4?t=1660924251\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong><i>NOTICE: Save data from the Ember Crusade IV Demo will carry over to the full game.</i></strong><br><br>Ember Crusade IV is a twin stick looter shooter roguelike where you embark on a blazing crusade to save the solar system from a demonic invasion.<br><br>Collect<strong> hundreds of guns, armor and materials</strong> to create the ultimate crusader. Take to the randomly generated battlefield, dodge rolling, shooting, reloading and pulverizing your enemies into a<i> very fine bloody pâté</i>. Ember Crusade IV features:<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong> Visceral combat</strong><br></li><li><strong> 7 Planets</strong><br></li><li> <strong>Hundreds of guns</strong><br></li><li> <strong>3 Powerful crusaders</strong></li></ul><br>Fight through seven distinct planets as one of three powerful crusaders: The <strong>Justicar</strong>, <strong>Marauder </strong>and <strong>Gunmancer</strong>. Each crusader brings a unique ability to the battlefield, like throwing holy hammers at enemies, or summoning guns made out of bone to fight alongside you.",
